Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:32.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,nevideli ste...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.37,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Neboj sa, všetko bude v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nevideli ste niekde malého chlapca?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.76,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musí byť stále na toalete...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:06.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Východ je rovno pred vami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prosím, zachovajte pokoj a nezastavujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, ty tam, vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to tam nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,No ták, tam vzadu je to nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Všetko je tam v plameňoch\N kvôli zemetraseniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musíš sa evakuovať do západného krídla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:09.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ale ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zemetrasenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To bolo dosť nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.63,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak to toto nazývam tesnotka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem vám veľmi pekne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie si ty to dievča z...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.06,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Môžeš vstať?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:02.52,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.48,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Východ je tam, všetci, ponáhľajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nebola si so svojim bratom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:09.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Išiel na toaletu celkom sám...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A čo tvoji rodičia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.57,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Východ je tam, všetci, ponáhľajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.16,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Východ je tam, všetci, ponáhľajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.83,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prišli sme sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.41,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Východ je tam, všetci, ponáhľajte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musím ho nájsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si dobrá sestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:37.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nechala som ho ísť samého... na toaletu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hľadala si ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno, ale nikde som ho nenašla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako sa volá?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.19,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako sa volá tvoj brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nájdeme tvojho brata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.08,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.34,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:27.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sú zranení.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Predsa len, bolo to dosť silné zemetrasenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.78,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,nevideli ste tu malého chlapca?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.33,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Má okolo sedem alebo osem rokov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Videli sme tu malých chlapcov,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.29,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale všetci boli so svojimi rodičmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, že sme vám nemohli pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie, vďaka aj tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte, nevideli ste tu malého chlapca?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je takto vysoký,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a má sedem alebo osem rokov...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:06.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mal na sebe žltozelené tričko\N s pásmi na hrudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to môj brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.15,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáčte.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nikde sme ho nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Videli sme pár chlapcov na prvom \Nposchodí v hračkárstve—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vážne?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:21.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme nájsť iné schody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tieto vyzerajú nebezpečne.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:55.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:25.02,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poď.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:35.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Už nikdy nesprav nič tak unáhlené, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.07,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Neuvedomuješ si, že je to tu nebezpečné?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale Yuuki môže byť v tom hračkárstve—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja viem,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.74,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale všetko bude zbytočné, ak sa zraníš aj ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.79,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ak sa zraním {\i1}aj ja{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:52.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ako to môžeš povedať? \NAko môžeš vedieť, že je zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.21,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to tam nebezpečné!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Stoj!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:07.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie! Pusti ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:11.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prepáč.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.06,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak som to nemyslela.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoj brat je určite v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.53,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pôjdem ho s tebou hľadať,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak ťa prosím, už nikdy nerob nič unáhlene, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:28.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.42,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.25,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Už to skoro je!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:37.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Raz, dva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.01,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je niekto z vás zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sme v poriadku,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:29.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,ale je to tu nebezpečné a mali by ste odísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:32.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hľadáme malého chlapca.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:35.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mal na sebe žltozelené tričko...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:40.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prehľadali sme celú oblasť, a toto \Nje jediné dieťa, ktoré sme našli.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.90,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Všetky ostatné sú pravdepodobne...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki, kde si?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Odpovedz mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:59.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki! Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:09.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme nateraz von.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.26,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Aj tu je to nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:13.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musíme odísť predtým, než sa\N to tu všetko zaplní dymom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty môžeš odísť, ak chceš!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale ja tu Yuukiho nemôžem nechať!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Potom uvažuj.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:22.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo by urobil, keby bol nažive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:25.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ak Yuuki žije,\N odišiel by rovnako ako ostatní.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.03,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A preto tu nesmieš zomrieť!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.99,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musíš prežiť a nájsť Yuukiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Keď už sme pri tom, kúp niečo na pitie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.22,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nápoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.27,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kam ideš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.94,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prosím, nechaj ma sa tu porozhliadnuť!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.41,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:11.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je tam niekto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.37,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pomoc, som tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prosím, pomôžte mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hneď to bude.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.50,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si to {\i1}ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:28.47,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.93,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Si zranený?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:34.18,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vydrž, o chvíľu ťa dostaneme von!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:34.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zdvihni to tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:37.14,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dobre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:43.98,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.57,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu, že si v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.91,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sestrička!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prší.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Počkáme, kým prestane?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to tu nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.30,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Horí?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:17.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tu by sme mohli zostať v suchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:43.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:46.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Vďakabohu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.88,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.35,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nefunguje?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.10,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.73,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ani mne nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Siete sú asi preťažené.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.40,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ako už bolo povedané,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.95,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ohromné zemetrasenie dnes postihlo región Kanto približne o 15:46,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:18.70,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}čiže pred asi 4 hodinami
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:22.08,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Epicentrum sa nachádza v severnej časti Tokyo Bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.21,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}približne 25 km pod morom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:27.46,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Magnitúda zemetrasenia,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.13,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}je odhadovaná na 8.0 Richterovej stupnice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.13,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,8.0?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:32.80,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Prosím, majte na pamäti možný výskyt dotrasov a prílivových vĺn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:34.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozrime si to tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.68,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dôsledkom zemetrasenia...
Comment: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pozrime si to tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoj telefón funguje?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.76,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}... hromadná doprava bola na dobu neurčitú odstavená. O stave vás budeme informovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:45.10,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Informácie od požiarneho zboru v Tokiu naznačujú, že veľké časti Tokia sú v plameňoch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.73,M8-Overlap,,0,0,0,,{\an9}Odporúča sa evakuácia všetkých obyvateľov...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kto vie, či je mama a otec v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.32,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Kde bývate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pri Kinuta Parku v Setagay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:56.24,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tak to je blízko Seijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.95,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja bývam v Sangenjay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.45,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Sakra, vôbec to nefunguje.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:04.04,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Myslím, že funguje iba 1seg. \N {\fs36}TL Note: Operátor
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Teraz nám nezostáva nič iné, iba čakať,\N ako sa toto celé vyvinie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Zatiaľ vymyslím spôsob, ako sa dostaneme domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Prečo si na nás tak milá?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:19.05,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie je to povinnosťou každého človeka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:19.97,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Iba žartujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:26.23,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tvoja sestra bola naozaj zúfalá, len aby ťa našla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:27.31,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to dobrá sestra, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je, vďaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:36.49,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musíme sa dostať domov čo najskôr, aby ste mohli mame dať ten darček.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:42.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Keď tak premýšľam, ešte som vám nepovedala ako sa volám, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.16,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Volám sa Mari Kusakabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ty si Yuuki a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.17,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Moje meno je Mirai Onozawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.71,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Takže "Mirai", že?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.09,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Pekné meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.80,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mne sa moc nepáči.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:00.85,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mne sa páči,{\i1}sestrička.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:02.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chodíš na základnú?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.81,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Chodí do siedmeho ročníka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.89,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,A čo ty, Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Do tretieho.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:12.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Musíte spolu naozaj dobre vychádzať, \Nkeď vás rodičia pustia bez dozoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.69,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ani nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Všetko je to {\i1}jej{\i0} chyba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:22.28,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mama sa vždy vyhovára na prácu, len aby nemusela ísť s nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To mi je ľúto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ja žijem s mojou matkou a dcérou,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:34.59,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,a vždy som tak zaneprázdnená prácou,\Nže sa nemôžem postarať o svoju dcérku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Naozaj zbožňuje hojdanie,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:44.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,tak sa naozaj snažím, aby sme sa mohli presťahovať do domu, kde sa môže hojdať.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:50.52,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale ak mi to bude trvať takto dlho,\N skorej vyrastie z hojdačiek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Skoro som zabudla.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:55.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Idem po niečo. \N Hneď sa vrátim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:57.36,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Neďaleko mám zaparkovanú motorku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:05.66,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Možno sa nevráti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.77,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nevráti sa, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.48,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Asi išla domov.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:38.53,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nemá povinnosť sa o nás starať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.62,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,To je v poriadku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:47.58,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nazýva sa to dotras;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.75,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,takéto niečo sa stáva\N po naozaj veľkom zemetrasení.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.54,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tento bol slabý,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.46,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,takže by sme tu mali byť v bezpečí.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.96,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nie ste hladní?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:01.55,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mám trochu koláča.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.68,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Tadá!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.43,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.72,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,No, chutiť bude stále rovnako.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.56,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Má narodeniny?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:17.82,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej, dnes má moje dievčatko narodeniny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.11,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Dnes oslavuje štyri roky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.57,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.40,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.86,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Nech sa páči.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.12,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ďakujem
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.70,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Je to dobré!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.00,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Trochu sa rozpadá.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.87,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Ale aj tak je okrúhly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:38.67,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Mám rada okrúhle koláče.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.92,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.64,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Čo budeme robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.39,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.44,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Najprv si oddýchnime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Som si istá, že zajtrajšok bude rušný.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.61,M8-Default,,0,0,0,,Áno.
